verbose_text: In group B and C, the RA content in the RPE - choroid complex of the eyes of guinea pigs with LIM was 12.40 +/-0.31 ng/100 mg and 12.33 +/-0.23 ng/100 mg, respectively before LIM, and significantly increased to 137.85 +/-1.02 ng/100 mg and 132.09 +/-0.44 ng/100 mg on the 14th day.
